Ravel Morrison has risked the wrath of West Ham supporters after the controversial midfielder posted a picture of himself on Instagram wearing an Arsenal shirt.

But he was quick to tweet a message to calm any irate Hammers fans, insisting he loves his current club and the manner in which they have stood by him.

He wrote: 'West Ham is I'm [sic] my (heart) Love the Club and the way the have stood by me.' 

